        "Antacids, iron, and calcium reduce absorption: give 2h before or 6h after doxycycline.",
        "Photosensitivity: avoid prolonged sun exposure during treatment.",
        "No dose adjustment required in renal insufficiency."
      ],
      "ajustesEspeciais": {
